{"tid":404041,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有啲港女真係好多事","createTime":"2017-09-17T16:44:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-19T13:48:29.000Z","uid":148011,"like":2261,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b95404002a707f4bfd330bb7f3b1419e4459178","tid":404041,"uid":148011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T16:44:22.000Z","msg":"頭先自己一個食飯，有對八婆搭枱坐正喺我隔離。<br />\n<br />\n我好快就叫咗個餐，有湯有飯。<br />\n對八婆就揀極都揀唔到，最後叫咗一份野食share。<br />\n<br />\n我個飯黎咗之後，佢地就好大聲咁講，<br />\n咁大份餐比着我自己一個一定食唔晒囉，女仔點會食到咁多野呀，我地share食先啱啱好囉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大佬，我大食關你春事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後佢地開始望住我碟飯品評每一樣材料，話我啲餸核突，接受唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後我個例湯黎咗，佢地又即刻話，比着我一定唔會飲呢啲味精湯囉，又熱又唔健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如是者佢我每夾一舊餸，每黎一樣野佢地都係咁大聲討論，直到我食完餐飯為止。<br />\n<br />\n我想問佢地係當我聾，定係想比說話我聽？連人地餐飯你都要管埋，監視住我食晒成餐飯，你地老母有無教你地禮貌？大家都係女人，點解食餐飯都要逼害我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf2d9324851e28c2629e2aaa031121df7bda515","tid":404041,"uid":125873,"like":469,"dislike":3,"score":466,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T16:49:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 純想知你係咪好肥 <br />\n<br />\n我係你會望住佢兩個笑幾吓 照道理會自動收嗲"},{"pid":"268739c6a1b0ffc0cd3a8100bb562777dc317bf4","tid":404041,"uid":148011,"like":829,"dislike":3,"score":826,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T16:57:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 純想知你係咪好肥 <br />\n<br />\n我係你會望住佢兩個笑幾吓 照道理會自動收嗲</blockquote><br />\nBMI 18<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ea03903c50204914d0df04c2a353aea5bb37aba","tid":404041,"uid":43114,"like":96,"dislike":7,"score":89,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T17:00:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 純想知你係咪好肥 <br />\n<br />\n我係你會望住佢兩個笑幾吓 照道理會自動收嗲</blockquote><br />\nBMI 18<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0cb6ac4005dc513e04defeeaa6f477aa99338d9","tid":404041,"uid":60563,"like":127,"dislike":1,"score":126,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T17:01:38.000Z","msg":"你係咪連望佢地一眼既膽都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"955056a806ccd44302146dd1651db3b71ee61382","tid":404041,"uid":148011,"like":189,"dislike":1,"score":188,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T17:06:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係咪連望佢地一眼既膽都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我有兜口兜面望過幾次，坐對面條女即刻望翻佢個friend繼續討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好撚無賴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0728a2ef3482802199a6e8297d8f0676db70f248","tid":404041,"uid":11143,"like":156,"dislike":3,"score":153,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T17:10:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec052f0d8e8b960a4364853f099f963a8b3c5115","tid":404041,"uid":126648,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T17:12:38.000Z","msg":"當面屌佢"},{"pid":"92bc8a4eb0ee6d1c3612d6ef2cf7acce3c06b4d9","tid":404041,"uid":142509,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T17:16:37.000Z","msg":"拍枱屌佢老母啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過佢一句 唔係講緊你就收皮<br />\n所以樓豬好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a7bc2bf1de740f9775c0fc42f43b2a7f06a633","tid":404041,"uid":148011,"like":174,"dislike":2,"score":172,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T17:18:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當面屌佢</blockquote><br />\n你地估條條女都係戰鬥民族黎架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa35caa1640664af91c1fced0f29f44aa77772d","ti